    "content": "The following table shows the target hardware for the application projects. | Project Name | Board | . | sam_a5d2_xult.X | SAMA5D2 Xplained Ultra Evaluation Kit | . |   |   | . Setting up SAMA5D2 Xplained Ultra Evaluation Kit . Setting up the board . | To run this demo two SAMA5D2 Xplained Ultra Evaluation Kit are required. One will be progammed as SPI master and other will be programmed as SPI slave. | Short jumper JP2 (DEBUG_DIS) on each board | Connect Pin 15, 16, 17, 18 on EXT1 of SPI slave to Pin 15, 16, 17, 18 on EXT1 of SPI master . | Pin 15 - SPI Chip Select | Pin 16 - MOSI | Pin 17 - MISO | Pin 18 - SCK | . | Connect Pin 9 on EXT1 of SPI slave to Pin 9 on EXT1 of SPI master. Pin 9 is configured as GPIO and serves as the slave busy pin. | Connect the Debug USB port on the board to the computer using a micro USB cable | . ",
