    "doc": "TC compare mode",
    "title": "Description",
    "content": "Three TC channels are configured in compare mode. Each channel generates different output waveform depending upon configured action on compare match and period match. Active low output: Output is set high on compare match A and is set low on compare match C. Active high output: Output is set low on compare match A and is set high on compare match C. Toggle output: Output toggles on compare match A. ",
